FORRT Contributor Analyses

 

As of 16 August 2025, FORRT has a total of 90 completed or ongoing projects and support teams, with a total of 586 contributors. There is an average (mean) of 2.44 contributions per person across all FORRT projects, and the average number of contributors per project is 15.60. You can see the full list of FORRT contributors and their individual contributions here.
